<br>
FA2 is pretty pointless now. 9 points for a 60% heal, with a 10 second timer...as if my shaman/healer hasn't given me a heal by then. Not totally useless (used mine to good effect today, when healer died and we got hit by a second wave of hibs before we could recover) but hardly worth 9 points imo.<br>
<br>
So basically IP costs 23 points, with no other real benefit. That's a LOT of passive abilities. With resistances on SC armor and RvR healing improvements I haven't really felt the need for it so far. <br>
<br>
The only problem I see is that we really don't have any good alternative RA's. Mastery of Pain is not worth taking above II because of the 50% crit cap in RvR. Parrying really isn't that hot. Our class RA is worthless.<br>
<br>
Purge is looking pretty good right now.<br>
<br>
